Package: nextword
Title: Next Word Prediction Using N-grams
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("First", "Last", , "first.last@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "YOUR-ORCID-ID"))
Description: A package for predicting the next word in a text sequence using
    n-gram language models. Provides functions to create n-grams from text
    corpora, compute frequencies, and predict likely next words based on
    input phrases.
License: `use_mit_license()`, `use_gpl3_license()` or friends to pick a
    license
